defs.value: fn <'a> (&'a mut self, time_format: String) -> &'a mut ConfigBuilder

defs.docs: Set offset used for logging time (default is 0)

defs.value: fn <'a> (&'a mut self, local: bool) -> &'a mut ConfigBuilder
defs.docs: set if you log in local timezone or UTC (default is UTC)

defs.name: add_filter_allow_str
defs.value: fn <'a> (&'a mut self, time_format: &'static str) -> &'a mut ConfigBuilder
defs.docs:
Add allowed module filters.
 If any are specified, only records from modules starting with one of these entries will be printed

defs.name: add_filter_allow
defs.value: fn <'a> (&'a mut self, time_format: String) -> &'a mut ConfigBuilder
defs.docs:
Add allowed module filters.
 If any are specified, only records from modules starting with one of these entries will be printed

defs.name: clear_filter_allow
defs.docs:
Clear allowed module filters.
 If none are specified, nothing is filtered out

defs.name: add_filter_ignore_str
defs.value: fn <'a> (&'a mut self, time_format: &'static str) -> &'a mut ConfigBuilder
defs.docs:
Add denied module filters.
 If any are specified, records from modules starting with one of these entries will be ignored

defs.name: add_filter_ignore
defs.value: fn <'a> (&'a mut self, time_format: String) -> &'a mut ConfigBuilder
defs.docs:
Add denied module filters.
 If any are specified, records from modules starting with one of these entries will be ignored

defs.name: clear_filter_ignore
defs.docs:
Clear ignore module filters.
 If none are specified, nothing is filtered
